The N4 toll road near Ngodwana claimed another three lives this morning. This is according to Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison spokesperson, Moeti Mmusi. The department released a statement this morning. Mmusi said, “A Kia Picanto hatchback overturned. The deceased were all passengers who died at the scene.” ALSO READ: Accessorise your vehicle at your own peril “One person was slightly injured while another one sustained critical injuries.” ALSO READ: Tow truckers arrested with money allegedly lifted from accident on N4 Mmusi added that it appears the driver may have lost control before the vehicle overturned. Read more in the next print edition.